{"tid":2250623,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"醫生係燈神","createTime":"2020-10-20T08:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:50:40.000Z","uid":179065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"285ed5c5211d0dcde49596789ffc4d86c9283eb6","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:29:30.000Z","msg":"胃痛左兩日，今日第三日終於請假去睇醫生啦。<br />\n原本就好地地keep住少少胃痛同all咁樣，入去睇既時候：<br />\n醫生問：你有冇發燒啊，有冇發冷啊？<br />\n我話：冇啊冇啊其實都冇咩事既，只係一直都個肚痛痛地。<br />\n醫生咁就冇開其他藥比我啦，淨係啲腸胃炎藥。<br />\n結果番到屋企黎料啦，食屎38.1度，又開始發冷，咁我又冇比到退燒藥食，咪唯有訓個覺唸住訓醒會退燒囉，結果宜家訓咗4個鐘，38.7度，又冇退燒藥食，我究竟好唔好宜家去多次睇醫生呢？<br />\n我好唔想再沖多次涼啊頂你，醫生你做咩燈我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a6f01b45d08ff7f477d4906d77df690ba726b3","tid":2250623,"uid":230502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"094254dbcfd83a7c410894d4d55f4dfc452b27a3","tid":2250623,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"發燒就睇醫生，發高燒好易腦膜炎死"},{"pid":"de58bba279c7337cced1d677ce7952d43b168533","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21a6f01b45d08ff7f477d4906d77df690ba726b3","tid":2250623,"uid":230502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"285ed5c5211d0dcde49596789ffc4d86c9283eb6","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:29:30.000Z","msg":"胃痛左兩日，今日第三日終於請假去睇醫生啦。<br />\n原本就好地地keep住少少胃痛同all咁樣，入去睇既時候：<br />\n醫生問：你有冇發燒啊，有冇發冷啊？<br />\n我話：冇啊冇啊其實都冇咩事既，只係一直都個肚痛痛地。<br />\n醫生咁就冇開其他藥比我啦，淨係啲腸胃炎藥。<br />\n結果番到屋企黎料啦，食屎38.1度，又開始發冷，咁我又冇比到退燒藥食，咪唯有訓個覺唸住訓醒會退燒囉，結果宜家訓咗4個鐘，38.7度，又冇退燒藥食，我究竟好唔好宜家去多次睇醫生呢？<br />\n我好唔想再沖多次涼啊頂你，醫生你做咩燈我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:33:22.000Z","msg":"唔好燈我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頭先番屋企唱左幾首歌，係肺炎既話全家有曬架啦"},{"pid":"c929167af0d89b6678795267f807a3a1a291e961","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"094254dbcfd83a7c410894d4d55f4dfc452b27a3","tid":2250623,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"發燒就睇醫生，發高燒好易腦膜炎死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:34:30.000Z","msg":"你覺得食必理痛有冇用啊，但係又好似唔太好同醫生處方既藥一齊食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好攰啊唔想沖多次涼，醫生燈神"},{"pid":"ccc54257a6cef3dbd92a8f005fca511b4df04916","tid":2250623,"uid":230502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af55b54df88546a8a46ab68bf0e8ca76f7c3d415","tid":2250623,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"柯哂就唔會發燒 發燒因為你未柯清 食粒panadol先啦"},{"pid":"6e7eff7ba0c198498f170643ee05f48b2429c86d","tid":2250623,"uid":68236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"094254dbcfd83a7c410894d4d55f4dfc452b27a3","tid":2250623,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"發燒就睇醫生，發高燒好易腦膜炎死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:42:23.000Z","msg":"幾十年前先會有咁既謬誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n腦膜炎會發高燒同壞腦<br />\n腸胃炎發燒係唔會導致腦膜炎同壞腦<br />\n除非佢屙嘔得勁食唔到野脫水死<br />\n<br />\n樓主真係燒得辛苦就食粒必理痛啦<br />\n唔係就飲多啖水就ok"},{"pid":"3ed876e0a01533f3afc6ed41d35058f9097f2a24","tid":2250623,"uid":68236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c929167af0d89b6678795267f807a3a1a291e961","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"094254dbcfd83a7c410894d4d55f4dfc452b27a3","tid":2250623,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"發燒就睇醫生，發高燒好易腦膜炎死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:34:30.000Z","msg":"你覺得食必理痛有冇用啊，但係又好似唔太好同醫生處方既藥一齊食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好攰啊唔想沖多次涼，醫生燈神"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:46:31.000Z","msg":"如果唔係屙得辛苦既建議你止屙藥都唔好食，等身體自然屙清佢，飲佢俾嗰啲電解質粉沖水飲，燒得辛苦可以食必理痛，睇真啲醫生係咪真係無開任何paracetamol/acetaminophen先呀如果duplicate 會傷肝"},{"pid":"950f3f58f15d1201ed986d608c4184c04f7dbebd","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ed876e0a01533f3afc6ed41d35058f9097f2a24","tid":2250623,"uid":68236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c929167af0d89b6678795267f807a3a1a291e961","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"094254dbcfd83a7c410894d4d55f4dfc452b27a3","tid":2250623,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"發燒就睇醫生，發高燒好易腦膜炎死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:34:30.000Z","msg":"你覺得食必理痛有冇用啊，但係又好似唔太好同醫生處方既藥一齊食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好攰啊唔想沖多次涼，醫生燈神"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:46:31.000Z","msg":"如果唔係屙得辛苦既建議你止屙藥都唔好食，等身體自然屙清佢，飲佢俾嗰啲電解質粉沖水飲，燒得辛苦可以食必理痛，睇真啲醫生係咪真係無開任何paracetamol/acetaminophen先呀如果duplicate 會傷肝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"咁我食必理痛算了唔食腸胃炎藥，thank you你啊<br />\n雖然我都唔知醫生同我開咗啲咩藥，但係好似冇電解質粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明我都唔係好屙咋嘛，點解要搞成咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541df4c5bc5df126ec0d70419241e7ae00239156","tid":2250623,"uid":242576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:57:34.000Z","msg":"腸胃炎啲菌未清係會發燒㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次腸胃炎睇醫生 佢都會問埋有冇燒<br />\n就算冇都會畀定退燒藥"},{"pid":"7dfcf6c94438ccfd48c4b739d3af8cb2e2b384ca","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"541df4c5bc5df126ec0d70419241e7ae00239156","tid":2250623,"uid":242576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:57:34.000Z","msg":"腸胃炎啲菌未清係會發燒㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次腸胃炎睇醫生 佢都會問埋有冇燒<br />\n就算冇都會畀定退燒藥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"可能因為佢想減少支出所以唔比退燒藥我掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又屙左次，好辣啊我個屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放過我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a97d0ba91e2820248cffdbab5f7eae9458d910","tid":2250623,"uid":366089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會係細菌入血？發燒同感染有關，特別你又腸胃炎緊，可能細菌入腸。<br />\n利申學護"},{"pid":"7d8a60814c4bf3402dcc34690be701b1fc2de6a6","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85a97d0ba91e2820248cffdbab5f7eae9458d910","tid":2250623,"uid":366089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會係細菌入血？發燒同感染有關，特別你又腸胃炎緊，可能細菌入腸。<br />\n利申學護"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:41:41.000Z","msg":"咁我應該點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，算啦我都係食必理痛等聽日再去睇醫生攞多日架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲燒死都唔退，好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c46952919a29fc94a07e9b70df2e1084b699955","tid":2250623,"uid":366089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:45:09.000Z","msg":"睇醫生，如果理定係細菌感染佢會開抗生素俾你，唔想睇可以叫屋企人去藥房買paracetamol 500mg，5毫子一粒，發燒高過38.5度就食一粒，6-8小時一次"},{"pid":"5469e1891f17d1efa0c073b6a45c6f47d3c0ef7e","tid":2250623,"uid":366089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"低過38.5度唔好食，多飲水同休息，保持散熱，因為發現可以幫免疫細胞提升活性"},{"pid":"5dbd7498ab08f954ab9e5c7e0f0860b781ca07ca","tid":2250623,"uid":366089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:47:29.000Z","msg":"好多錯字，sorry"},{"pid":"85bcd494fb4947de20b310227858cab193585053","tid":2250623,"uid":179065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5469e1891f17d1efa0c073b6a45c6f47d3c0ef7e","tid":2250623,"uid":366089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite